chunk_content: Data entered by: This data should be entered in DATIM by the USG country team. Guiding narrative 1. Does the host country TX_CURR result assume an IIT/LTFU definition of <28 days or <90 days? questions: Describe the data systems and methods of aggregation used at the national and subnational levels to report treatment data. 2. Outline any work that the host country government has done to ensure that the reported figures are accurate (i.e., data quality assessments, results adjustment, etc.). 3. Discuss progress towards aligning host-country age/sex disaggregations to standard five-year age and sex bands? 4. For targets, please describe the host country target setting process.
